Scribners, 1932. 1st Edition. Hardcover. Near Fine / Very Good. Item #1804112

Near fine first edition with "A" present on copyright page; date on title page matches date on copyright page. Rubbing at top and bottom of spine, light edge wear. Very minor rips and folds on several pages. In very good minus dust jacket with original price, $3.50, listed on front flap. Detached from front cover at spine hinge, slightly tanned edges. Housed in custom-made slipcase.
